Package jwebminer2

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnalysisProcessor
    The class that performs web searches, calculates corresponding statistics makes the results available.
    FeatureValueFileSaver
    Objects of this class are used by ResultsReportPanels (or other classes) to perform actual saving of data in a variety of formats.
    Main
    Runs the jWebMiner software.
    SearchStringFileParser
    An implementation of the ListInputParser interface for use by the ListInputPanel class in choosing and parsing of files.
